ntroducing a full-stack web development project that brings the magic of Netflix to life! This responsive and feature-rich web application leverages the Netflix API to provide users with a captivating experience. Built with React and Next.js, it offers a seamless and visually appealing way to explore Netflix's vast movie library.

Key Features:

Netflix API Integration: Our project taps into the Netflix API to access an extensive database of movies and TV shows. Users can search for their favorite content and discover new releases effortlessly.

Responsive Design: The web application is meticulously designed to adapt seamlessly to various screen sizes, ensuring a delightful user experience on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

Movie Details: Users can access comprehensive movie details, including titles, genres, ratings, descriptions, cast and crew information, and release dates. Dive deep into the world of each film.
